---
title: Asian Chicken Schnitzels & Garlic Rice with Teriyaki Veggies & Aioli
description: Give chicken schnitzel an Asian-style twist by serving it with garlic aioli for dipping, plus a side of teriyaki veggies. It's such a
crowd-pleasing combo that you'd better prepare for repeat requests!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/asian-chicken-schnitzel-rice-bowl-5ee9ef74.jpg
